👨‍🍳🥧🍕 @jamieoliver 's REVERSE PUFF PASTRY PIZZA 👨‍🍳🥧🍕
(Pls follow My stories for the process)
Uses @emborgasia 's vegan mozzarella.
Uses @alcenerosg 's organic extra virgin olive oil and balsamic glaze.
.
This is a great way to use your leftover veg in the fridge or freezer. You can use whatever veg you have on hand. The key elements are tomatoes, onion and garlic. The rest is just a balance of colors.
.
You can get the full recipe on the link at my profile. And as always, thank you very much for your kind support. 🙏
.
